      "value": "<h1>Computer Idol</h1>\n<p>A&nbsp;computer idol&nbsp;is a small statuette that creates a field of good luck during computer use. These figures vary wildly in shape, from religious figures to trivid mascots. When you fail a Computers check, the&nbsp;computer idol&nbsp;allows you to reroll and take the higher result. You must be within 5 feet of your&nbsp;computer idol&nbsp;and able to see it to benefit from it.</p>\n<p>A&nbsp;computer idol&nbsp;allows a number of rerolls per day based on its type. Once you benefit from a given&nbsp;computer idol, you canâ€™t benefit from a different one for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Two rerolls</strong></p>"
